window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>She is destined to soar with the dragons, but first...she needs to be chosen.</b></p> <p><b>An epic dragon-riding adventure from Jada Fisher, author of the popular Dragon Oracle series.</b></p> <p>Eist was born to be a dragon rider; she just knows it. When fate conspires to take her parents and leave her orphaned and injured, her future appears bleak. Unwilling to back down, she must overcome a system stacked against her. Even if she passes all the tests, there’s no guarantee she will ever fly on a dragon. Can she beat the odds and find her destiny, or will she be stranded on the ground?</p> <p>The <i>Chosen Omnibus </i>contains the first three stories in the Brindle Dragon series, which follows the story of a young girl and her most unusual dragon as they set out to defeat an evil they don’t even know exists yet.</p> <p>Download the <i>Chosen Omnibus</i> and get started on your next epic adventure today!</p>"; 
